{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260313033355b3386300928747ff","session_id":"6b971ac8-f58b-4539-b600-b41cd157b86c","message":{"id":"20260313033355b3386300928747ff","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All four steps are complete. Here's a summary of what was created for F-011 (AI CLI Proxy):\n\n## ✅ F-011 AI CLI Proxy - Planning Complete\n\n### Files Created\n\n| File | Size | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| `context-snapshot.md` | 34KB | Team knowledge base with project structure, Prizm context, and source files |\n| `spec.md` | 9.5KB | Feature specification with user stories, acceptance criteria, and requirements |\n| `plan.md` | 19KB | Technical implementation plan with architecture, interfaces, and data models |\n| `tasks.md` | 19.5KB | Task breakdown with 44 tasks across 4 phases |\n\n### Key Deliverables\n\n**Feature Scope:**\n- Natural language task execution via AI CLI\n- Multi-turn conversation context preservation\n- `/stop` command to interrupt AI CLI tasks\n- Heartbeat progress notifications for long-running tasks\n- Telegram MarkdownV2 output formatting\n- User-friendly error handling with recovery suggestions\n\n**Architecture Highlights:**\n- New `src/services/ai-cli-service.js` - Core service for AI CLI execution\n- New `src/utils/markdown-v2-formatter.js` - Telegram formatting utility\n- Extended `src/services/session-store.js` - Process tracking per session\n- Extended `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - AI CLI interrupt support\n- Config extensions: `AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_THRESHOLD_MS`, `AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS`, `AI_CLI_ENABLE_HEARTBEAT`\n\n**Task Summary:**\n- **Phase 1** (T-001~T-009): Setup & Foundation - 9 tasks, 6 parallelizable\n- **Phase 2** (T-010~T-029): Core Service - 13 tasks, 5 parallelizable  \n- **Phase 3** (T-030~T-049): Integration - 11 tasks, 3 parallelizable\n- **Phase 4** (T-050~T-060): Polish & Documentation - 11 tasks, 7 parallelizable\n\n**Total: 44 tasks, 21 can be parallelized**\n\n---\n\n**COMPLETION_SIGNAL**: