me\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:53.882Z\",\"pid\":40037,\"bin\":\"codebuddy\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"sleep 10 && echo done\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:53.985Z\",\"pid\":40037,\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process interrupted\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:53.986Z\",\"pid\":40037,\"code\":null,\"elapsedSec\":0,\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process closed\"}\n    ✖ should clear session store after interrupt (106.046542ms)\n  ✖ interruptAiCli (107.03125ms)\n  ▶ isAiCliRunning\n    ✔ should export isAiCliRunning function (0.10625ms)\n    ✔ should return false when no process running (0.0645ms)\n  ✔ isAiCliRunning (0.200542ms)\n  ▶ getActiveProcessInfo\n    ✔ should export getActiveProcessInfo function (0.055625ms)\n    ✔ should return null when no process running (0.055125ms)\n  ✔ getActiveProcessInfo (0.130833ms)\n  ▶ Error Handling\n    ✔ should return helpful error for process spawn failure (0.982542ms)\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:53.988Z\",\"bin\":\"non-existent-command-that-should-fail\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"test prompt\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:53.989Z\",\"pid\":40065,\"bin\":\"codebuddy\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"sleep 5\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:53.990Z\",\"code\":-2,\"elapsedSec\":0,\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process closed\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T19:43:54.093Z\",\"pid\":40065,\"code\":null,\"elapsedSec\":0,\"sessionId\":\"test-session-f011\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process closed\"}\n    ✔ should include suggestion on timeout (104.98ms)\n  ✔ Error Handling (106.03175ms)\n✖ F-011 AI CLI Service (41609.306417ms)\nℹ tests 17\nℹ suites 6\nℹ pass 16\nℹ fail 1\nℹ cancelled 0\nℹ skipped 0