{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260313035544ec74c409bd904ab0","session_id":"6b971ac8-f58b-4539-b600-b41cd157b86c","message":{"id":"20260313035544ec74c409bd904ab0","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Implementation complete. Let me provide a summary:\n\n---\n\n## COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n\n**Feature F-011 (AI CLI Proxy) implementation complete.**\n\n### Summary\n\nSuccessfully implemented all core tasks for F-011 AI CLI Proxy feature using TDD approach:\n\n### Files Created\n- `src/services/ai-cli-service.js` - Main AI CLI service with process tracking, streaming, heartbeat, and interrupt support\n- `src/utils/heartbeat-manager.js` - Reusable heartbeat utility\n- `src/utils/markdown-v2-formatter.js` - Telegram MarkdownV2 formatter\n- `tests/services/ai-cli-service.test.js` - 17 tests for AI CLI service\n- `tests/services/session-store-f011.test.js` - 10 tests for session store extensions\n- `tests/config/f011-config.test.js` - 7 tests for config fields\n- `tests/utils/heartbeat-manager.test.js` - 9 tests for heartbeat manager\n- `tests/utils/markdown-v2-formatter.test.js` - 23 tests for MarkdownV2 formatter\n\n### Files Modified\n- `src/config.js` - Added AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_THRESHOLD_MS, AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS, AI_CLI_ENABLE_HEARTBEAT\n- `src/services/session-store.js` - Added process tracking methods\n- `src/services/index.js` - Exported ai-cli-service functions\n- `src/bot/telegram.js` - Integrated AI CLI service with streaming, heartbeat, and MarkdownV2\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - Extended to handle AI CLI task interruption\n- `.env.example` - Added F-011 config documentation\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime.prizm` - Updated with F-011 entries\n\n### Test Results\n- **All F-011 specific tests pass** (66 tests)\n- Pre-existing baseline failures (22 tests) remain - unrelated to F-011:\n  - handleStatus returns status message\n  - T-101 through T-106 plan command tests\n  - planMeta, normalizePlanType\n  - INT-F001-US4-AC4.3 lint test\n  - US4 static checks\n  - US-3.1