`\n  50→- **Acceptance Criteria**:\n  51→  - getActiveProcess(sessionKey) returns process info or null\n  52→  - setActiveProcess(sessionKey, info) stores process info\n  53→  - updateProcessBytes(sessionKey, bytes) updates byte count\n  54→  - clearActiveProcess(sessionKey) removes process entry\n  55→  - clear(sessionKey) also clears active process\n  56→- **Complexity**: Medium\n  57→- **US**: US-3 (Task Interrupt)\n  58→\n  59→### T-004: [P] Create heartbeat manager utility [x]\n  60→- **Goal**: Create reusable heartbeat logic\n  61→- **Input**: F-011 heartbeat requirements\n  62→- **Output**: New heartbeat-manager.js utility\n  63→- **File**: `src/utils/heartbeat-manager.js`\n  64→- **Acceptance Criteria**:\n  65→  - startHeartbeat(callback, intervalMs) returns stop function\n  66→  - Heartbeat only triggers after thresholdMs elapsed\n  67→  - Stop function clears timer and resources\n  68→- **Complexity**: Low\n  69→- **US**: US-4 (Heartbeat Progress)\n  70→\n  71→### T-005: [P] Write unit tests for session-store extensions [x]\n  72→- **Goal**: Test process tracking methods\n  73→- **Input**: T-003 implementation\n  74→- **Output**: Test file for session-store F-011 features\n  75→- **File**: `tests/services/session-store-f011.test.js`\n  76→- **Acceptance Criteria**:\n  77→  - Test getActiveProcess/setActiveProcess\n  78→  - Test updateProcessBytes\n  79→  - Test clearActiveProcess\n  80→  - Test clear also clears process\n  81→- **Complexity**: Low\n  82→- **US**: US-3\n  83→\n  84→### T-006: Create MarkdownV2 formatter utility [x]\n  85→- **Goal**: Implement Telegram MarkdownV2 formatting\n  86→- **Input**: Telegram MarkdownV2 spec\n  87→- **Output**: New markdown-v2-formatter.js\n  88→- **File**: `src/utils/markdown-v2-formatter.js`\n  89→- **Acceptance Criteria**:\n  90→  - escapeMarkdownV2() escapes all required chars\n  91→  - formatCodeBlock() creates proper code blocks\n  92→  - convertToMarkdownV2() handles common markdown elements\n  93→  - splitRe