{"type":"user","uuid":"f443f7c4-f543-4652-b35e-605c615f7593","session_id":"6b971ac8-f58b-4539-b600-b41cd157b86c","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_5e4159a9a2734ff7b1bb05f4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# PrizmKit Feature Registry\n   2→\n   3→> Auto-generated by prizmkit-summarize. Do not edit manually.\n   4→\n   5→## Features\n   6→\n   7→### [001] Project Infrastructure Setup\n   8→- **Branch**: feat/F-001-project-infrastructure-setup\n   9→- **Status**: Complete\n  10→- **Date**: 2026-03-12\n  11→- **Key Files**:\n  12→  - `src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js` (loadAndValidateConfig batch validation)\n  13→  - `src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js` (DIRECTORY_CONVENTION, resolvePlansPaths)\n  14→  - `src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js` (EXIT_CODES constant)\n  15→  - `src/pipeline-infra/cli-entry.js` (NEW: reusable CLI entry wrapper)\n  16→  - `src/pipeline-infra/index.js` (updated re-exports)\n  17→  - `src/index.js` (startup config summary log)\n  18→  - `dev-pipeline/scripts/path_policy.py` (Python parity: DIRECTORY_CONVENTION, resolve_plans_paths)\n  19→  - `tsconfig.json` (expanded include to src/**/*.js)\n  20→  - `eslint.config.js` (added recommended rules baseline)\n  21→- **API Changes**: None (internal infrastructure only)\n  22→- **Data Changes**: None (configuration and path conventions only)\n  23→\n  24→---\n  25→\n  26→### [008] Commit Workflow Integration\n  27→- **Branch**: feat/F-008-commit-workflow-integration\n  28→- **Status**: Complete\n  29→- **Date**: 2026-03-12\n  30→- **Key Files**:\n  31→  - `src/services/git-service.js` (Git wrapper, status operations, commit/amend)\n  32→  - `src/services/commit-service.js` (Validation orchestration, commit recording, history retrieval)\n  33→  - `src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js` (Telegram /commit command handler)\n  34→  - `src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js` (Telegram /commits history command handler)\n  35→  - `test/` (Unit and integration tests for commit