026-03-12T20:01:10.903Z\",\"pid\":53745,\"bin\":\"echo\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"echo second message\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n[CodeBuddy:stdout] -p echo second message -y\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:10.904Z\",\"pid\":53745,\"code\":0,\"elapsedSec\":0,\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process closed\"}\n  ▶ Multi-turn Conversation\n    ✖ should maintain session context across executions (7.353584ms)\n  ✖ Multi-turn Conversation (7.510958ms)\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:10.909Z\",\"pid\":53751,\"bin\":\"sleep\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"10\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n[CodeBuddy:stderr] sleep: illegal option -- p\n[CodeBuddy:stderr] usage: sleep number[unit] [...]\n[CodeBuddy:stderr] Unit can be 's' (seconds, the default), m (minutes), h (hours), or d (days).\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:10.910Z\",\"pid\":53751,\"code\":1,\"elapsedSec\":0,\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process closed\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:11.012Z\",\"bin\":\"/nonexistent/binary/that/does/not/exist\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"test\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n  ▶ Stop Interrupt\n    ✖ should interrupt running process via /stop (102.87075ms)\n  ✖ Stop Interrupt (103.04575ms)\n  ▶ Error Handling\n    ✔ should handle process spawn failure gracefully (0.822541ms)\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:11.013Z\",\"pid\":53758,\"bin\":\"sh\",\"args\":[\"-p\",\"exit 1\",\"-y\"],\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process started\"}\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:11.015Z\",\"code\":-2,\"elapsedSec\":0,\"sessionId\":\"test-telegram-session-001\",\"msg\":\"AI CLI process closed\"}\n[CodeBuddy:stderr] sh: exit 1: No such file or directory\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":\"2026-03-12T20:01:11