{"type":"user","uuid":"3e08a9d8-732f-4758-9718-a67000afa474","session_id":"6b971ac8-f58b-4539-b600-b41cd157b86c","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_1d55b8453922435ab13673cb","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# Feature Specification: F-011 AI CLI Proxy\n   2→\n   3→**Feature ID**: F-011\n   4→**Feature Name**: AI CLI Proxy\n   5→**Slug**: 011-ai-cli-proxy\n   6→**Status**: Draft\n   7→**Created**: 2026-03-13\n   8→**Dependencies**: F-009 (General Command Executor - Completed)\n   9→\n  10→---\n  11→\n  12→## 1. Overview\n  13→\n  14→### 1.1 Description\n  15→将 AI CLI（cbc/codebuddy）作为智能代理层，用户用自然语言描述意图，Bot 调用 AI CLI 来理解并执行复杂任务。这是 PrizmClaw 区别于普通远程 shell 工具的核心差异化能力。\n  16→\n  17→### 1.2 Problem Statement\n  18→- 用户需要记住复杂的命令行参数和语法\n  19→- 简单任务需要多步操作，用户体验不流畅\n  20→- 缺乏智能化的任务理解和执行能力\n  21→- 长时间运行的任务缺乏进度反馈\n  22→\n  23→### 1.3 Goals\n  24→- 提供自然语言接口，降低使用门槛\n  25→- 支持多轮对话上下文保持\n  26→- 提供任务中断能力\n  27→- 实时进度反馈\n  28→- 正确的输出格式化\n  29→\n  30→---\n  31→\n  32→## 2. User Stories\n  33→\n  34→### US-1: 自然语言任务执行\n  35→**作为** 用户\n  36→**我想要** 用自然语言描述我的意图\n  37→**以便于** AI CLI 理解并执行复杂任务，无需记忆命令语法\n  38→\n  39→**验收标准**:\n  40→- AC-1.1: 用户发送自然语言消息后，Bot 调用 AI CLI 执行\n  41→- AC-1.2: 执行结果流式回传到 Telegram\n  42→- AC-1.3: 支持代码块、链接等 Markdown 元素正确渲染\n  43→\n  44→### US-2: 多轮对话上下文\n  45→**作为** 用户\n  46→**我想要** 在多轮对话中保持上下文\n  47→**以便于** 连续追问或补充指令，无需重复描述背景\n  48→\n  49→**验收标准**:\n  50→- AC-2.1: 会话上下文在多轮对话中保持\n  51→- AC-2.2: 用户可以追问或补充指令\n  52→- AC-2.3: 上下文根据 MAX_HISTORY_TURNS 配置自动裁剪\n  53→\n  54→### US-3: 任务中断\n  55→**作为** 用户\n  56→**我想要** 能够中断正在执行的 AI CLI 任务\n  57→**以便于** 在发现错误或改变主意时停止执行\n  58→\n  59→**验收标准**:\n  60→- AC-3.1: 提供 /stop 命令中断正在执行的 AI CLI 任务\n  61→- AC-3.2: 中断后返回确认消息\n  62→- AC-3.3: 中断需要适当权限（admin 或当前任务发起者）\n  63→\n  64→### US-4: 长任务进度反馈\n  65→**作为** 用户\n  66→**我想要** 在长时间运行的任务中看到进度反馈\n  67→**以便于** 知道任务正在执行，系统没有卡住\n  68→\n  69→**验收标准**:\n  70→- AC-4.1: 超过 HEARTBEAT_THRESHOLD_MS 的任务定期推送进度\n  71→- AC-4.2: 进度消息显示已执行时间和状态\n  72→- AC-4.3: 进度消息可配置（频率、内容）\n  73→\n  74→### US-5: 错误处理与恢复建议\n  75→**作为** 用户\n  76→**我想要** 在 AI CLI 异常时获得清晰的错误信息\n  77→**以便于** 了解问题原因并采取正确的恢复操作\n  78→\n  79→**验收标准**:\n  80→- AC-5.1: 进程异常退出时返回可理解的错误信息\n  81→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce3a32437d4af704548a467fd4021","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T20:18:46.561Z","_requestId":"39750009e8f3457a8b44aaadfd2ecc82"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260313041846d27bdfc8888a4c6b","session_id":"6b971ac8-f58b-4539-b600-b41cd157b86c","message":{"id":"20260313041846d27bdfc8888a4c6b","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me verify each acceptance criteria:\n\n**AC-1: Natural Language Execution** ✅\n- AI CLI service spawns CodeBuddy process with prompt\n- Stream publishing to Telegram implemented\n- MarkdownV2 formatting implemented\n\n**AC-2: Multi-turn Context** ✅\n- Session store maintains context\n- `toPrompt()` builds context for AI CLI\n- MAX_HISTORY_TURNS is respected\n\n**AC-3: Task Interrupt** ✅\n- `/stop` command extended to interrupt AI CLI tasks\n- Permission check implemented (`canInterruptAiCli`)\n- Confirmation message returned\n\n**AC-4: Heartbeat Progress** ✅\n- `heartbeat-manager.js` implements threshold-based heartbeat\n- Progress message shows elapsed time and bytes\n- Configurable via `AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_*` env vars\n\n**AC-5: MarkdownV2 Formatting** ✅\n- `markdown-v2-formatter.js` implements conversion\n- Code blocks, bold, italic, links handled\n- Special characters escaped\n\n**AC-6: Error Handling** ✅\n- Process spawn failure returns helpful message\n- Timeout includes suggestion about `/stop` or config\n- Non-zero exit includes stderr\n\nLet me mark T-060 as complete:"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce3a32437d4af704548a467fd4021","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T20:18:59.534Z","_requestId":"39750009e8f3457a8b44aaadfd2ecc82"}
